# Edume — Architecture Analysis

## Overview

**Edume** is a customizable e-learning platform built on the **VARK** (Visual, Aural, Read/Write, Kinesthetic) model, designed to tailor content delivery to individual learning styles. The tech stack is:

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | Static HTML pages + Vanilla CSS + Vanilla JS |
| Backend API | PHP (XAMPP) — JSON API endpoints |
| Database | MySQL (via `mysqli`) |
| Communication | AJAX (`XMLHttpRequest`) — JSON POST |
| Auth | PHP Sessions (`$_SESSION`) |
| Avatar | Gravatar API *(planned, not yet integrated)* |

---

## Project Structure

```
Edume/
├── index.html                  # Landing page (VARK intro videos, FAQ)
├── loginpage.html              # Combined Login / Register / Forgot-Password
├── questionnaire.html          # VARK Assessment Quiz (8 questions)
├── dashboard.html              # Student dashboard (sidebar + courses)
├── course.html                 # Course catalog (12 languages listed)
├── python.html                 # Python course player (chapters + resources)
├── coding.html                 # Coding Sandbox (multi-language editor)
├── profile.html                # Student profile (avatar, skills, bio)
│
├── dashboard_admin.html        # Admin dashboard (charts + stats)
├── course_manage_admin.html    # Admin course CRUD
├── user_manage_admin.html      # Admin user management
├── support_center_admin.html   # Admin support/report center
├── profile_admin.html          # Admin profile page
│
├── JS/                         # 13 JavaScript modules (one per page)
├── CSS/                        # 13 CSS files (one per page) + style.css
├── PHP/                        # 6 PHP API endpoints
├── database/                   # SQL schema files
├── image/                      # Static images & backgrounds
├── video/                      # Hero/promo videos
└── material/                   # Capstone Proposal PDF
```

