## Database Schema (14 Tables)

Defined in [edume_merged_schema.sql](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/database/edume_merged_schema.sql):

```mermaid
erDiagram
    users ||--o{ user_skills : has
    users ||--o{ user_progress : tracks
    users ||--o{ quiz_attempts : takes
    users ||--o{ user_achievements : earns
    users ||--o{ user_vark_results : assessed

    courses ||--o{ chapters : contains
    chapters ||--o{ chapter_objectives : lists
    chapters ||--o{ content_materials : holds
    chapters ||--o{ quizzes : includes
    chapters ||--o{ user_progress : tracks

    quizzes ||--o{ quiz_questions : contains
    quizzes ||--o{ quiz_attempts : attempted

    achievements ||--o{ user_achievements : awarded
    vark_questions ||--o{ vark_options : has
```

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `users` | Auth, role (student/admin), VARK style, profile |
| `user_skills` | Tags for student skill tracking |
| `courses` | Course catalog with VARK flags per style |
| `chapters` | Ordered lessons within a course |
| `chapter_objectives` | Learning objectives per chapter |
| `content_materials` | Videos, text, practice problems with `vark_tag` |
| `quizzes` / `quiz_questions` | MCQ quizzes per chapter |
| `quiz_attempts` | Student quiz score history |
| `user_progress` | Chapter completion + XP tracking |
| `achievements` / `user_achievements` | Gamification badges |
| `vark_questions` / `vark_options` | VARK assessment questionnaire (DB-driven) |
| `user_vark_results` | Per-dimension VARK scores |

