## Module Breakdown

### Student Module

| Page | JS File | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| **Landing** | [app.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/app.js) | VARK intro video hover-to-play, FAQ accordion |
| **Login** | [loginpage.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/loginpage.js) | Combined login/register with animated slide transitions, forgot-password flow (email verify → reset), AJAX to PHP, admin redirect logic |
| **VARK Quiz** | [questionnaire.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/questionnaire.js) | 8-question assessment (VA/R/K categories), progress bar, saves result via AJAX to [save_learning_style.php](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/PHP/save_learning_style.php) |
| **Dashboard** | [dashboard.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/dashboard.js) | Sidebar nav with collapse/mobile toggle, progress bars, course enrollment/resume, search, logout |
| **Courses** | [course.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/course.js) | 12-language catalog, enrollment via `localStorage`, page routing map |
| **Python Course** | [python.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/python.js) | 3-chapter course (Intro/Syntax/Output), VARK-filtered resources (VA=YouTube, R=text, K=practice), MCQ quiz engine, report form |
| **Coding Sandbox** | [coding.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/coding.js) | Multi-language editor (Python/JS/HTML/CSS/C++), simulated execution, line numbers, save/load via `localStorage` |
| **Profile** | [profile.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/profile.js) | Tab navigation, avatar upload with preview, inline edit for name/email/skills/bio, Gravatar-ready |

### Admin Module

| Page | JS File | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| **Dashboard** | [dashboard_admin.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/dashboard_admin.js) | Stats cards, VARK distribution chart (Chart.js doughnut), activity line chart, top courses, recent users, system health |
| **Course Mgmt** | [course_manage_admin.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/course_manage_admin.js) | 3-level drill-down (Courses → Subjects → Resources/Quizzes), full CRUD, image compression via Canvas API, JSON `localStorage` storage |
| **User Mgmt** | [user_manage_admin.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/user_manage_admin.js) | User list with search/filter, modal edit with change detection, delete with confirm, CSV export, auto-refresh |
| **Support** | [support_center_admin.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/support_center_admin.js) | Report table with pagination, status toggle (Pending ↔ Resolved), filter/search, mock data |
| **Profile** | [profile_admin.js](file:///d:/School/CapstoneProject/Edume/JS/profile_admin.js) | Tab nav, avatar upload, personal info edit, change password |

